title: 262 34 "Scramble over Robin! A Cunning Plan by Sniperking!!"Transliteration: "Robin sōdatsusen! Sogekingu no kisaku!!" (Japanese:ロビン争奪戦!そげキングの奇策!!) Yukihiko Nakao Hirohiko Kamisaka April 16, 2006(2006-04-16)[57][58] July 13, 2014
